      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent GCI analysis on three systematically refined meshes for hemolysis QOI at each operating point.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study was completed for velocity and pressure fields; hemolysis index GCI was computed only at operating point 3. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
