      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence must be demonstrated to residual levels below 1e-6 for all equations with solution sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitoring was not systematically documented across all operating points. Residual logs were not archived in the project record. This factor is flagged as an epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
