      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of simulation setup and post-processing scripts must be documented.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of CFD setup files or post-processing scripts was conducted. Single analyst performed all simulation configuration and result extraction. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity of hemolysis prediction to turbulence model selection and hemolysis constitutive law must be quantified with alternative model comparisons.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected without systematic comparison to alternative models (e.g., RSM, LES). Power-law hemolysis model coefficients were taken from Giersiepen et al. without uncertainty characterisation. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
