      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary conditions must have documented uncertainty distributions used as inputs to Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on flow rate and rotational speed inputs. Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients were treated as deterministic. Input uncertainty distributions were not sourced from literature with justification. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
